title.narrative: PROCOFSERVICES and P0165 for Helmand Support Project

description.narrative: This activity (PROCOFSERVICES and P0165 for Helmand Support Project) is a component of Helmand Support Project reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £1,187,933. This component benefits Afghanistan, and works in the following sector(s): Civilian peace-building, conflict prevention and resolution. The start date is 01-09-2008 and the end date is 31-03-2012.
